\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
One approach
\series default
 here that we can construct a possible 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 
\series bold
from its diagonalization
\series default
, given what we know of the eigenvalues and by 
\emph on
choosing
\emph default
