\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{A=X\Lambda X^{-1}=\underbrace{\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 1+i & 1-i\\
1 & i & -i\\
1 & -i & i
\end{array}\right)}_{X=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
x_{1} & x_{2} & x_{3}\end{array}\right)}\underbrace{\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
-1\\
 & 2i\\
 &  & -2i
\end{array}\right)}_{\Lambda}X^{-1}}.
\]

\end_inset

You were 
\emph on
not
\emph default
