\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x(t)=\underbrace{\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
v_{1} & v_{2} & v_{3}\end{array}\right)}_{V}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\cos(2t)\\
e^{-t}\\
\sin(2t)
\end{array}\right),
\]

\end_inset

which gives
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
